      "content": "{\n  \"cwd\": \"/Users/sam.zhang/Documents/codex-supervisor\",\n  \"execution_layer_policy\": {\n    \"agentic_lead_policy\": {\n      \"min_subagents\": 3,\n      \"policy\": \"off\",\n      \"required_evidence_grade\": \"self_reported\",\n      \"required_roles\": [],\n      \"solo_exception_for_artifact_only_gates\": false\n    },\n    \"allowed_dynamic_workflow_task_classes\": [],\n    \"codex_supervises_final_artifact\": true,\n    \"dynamic_workflow_task_class\": null,\n    \"lead_execution_layer\": \"single_lead_worker\",\n    \"mode\": \"lead_direct\",\n    \"preview_required_gates\": [],\n    \"supervision_layer\": \"codex_plus_lead\"\n  },\n  \"expected_decisions\": [],\n  \"expected_objections\": [],\n  \"expected_specialists\": [],\n  \"gate\": \"outcome_review\",\n  \"injected_lesson_block\": \"Known failure modes to verify before claiming\\nThese are advisory lessons from previous supervisor runs. They do not satisfy any gate by themselves.\\n1. [FM-1.1] Disobey task specification (source_run_id=40f4ecea-e8bd-4639-aec6-27d686743e8f): Repair the planning artifact or traceability gap before invoking the lead again.\\n2. [FM-1.5] Unaware of termination conditions (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Verify this known failure mode explicitly before claiming the gate is complete.\\n3. [FM-2.4] Information withholding (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Address independent reviewer objections with concrete evidence references.\\n4. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\\n5. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=d84b43e3-70de-4f95-b2dc-c7f9aca8684f): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\",\n  \"injected_lesson_block_sha256\": \"75a5d623043d555960ad6a3ef65d07dae2e4cc872346d43a7f0e2d8ba4db8e6b\",\n  \"injected_lesson_ids\": [\n    \"lesson-eb78dbaff424a8c1f8dd96b677ccdcb5dd267ca011698619ae37e54156f2eaab\",\n    \"lesson-49755707839e187f3a6fa0e4e84e237398d1457f2fe1421f8f1f53faa6cbbb9e\",\n    \"lesson-715f39df8c3dc22bea09092f80685d87f086d8cdbbf58a0ec008ce0e27d1cb38\",\n    \"lesson-c1ddc61a54fdf5f87bcf9f04ea6371210df0df2052ed0f17cd9aa372f56e375c\",\n    \"lesson-75f6bb3a7c6b9e406a22bac66b502bc9831a45773be490bb6ecb747735c19383\"\n  ],\n  \"instruction\": \"Supervisor-owned workflow gate: outcome_review.\\n\\nIntent:\\nRun hash-pinned AutoResearch evaluators as durable budget-enforced jobs and ship a replay-corpus reference evaluator as the default metric source.\\n\\nReview this gate against the current source artifacts and return a typed dual_agent_outcome.\\nUse decisions/objections to say whether the gate should accept, revise, or deny.\\n\\nKnown failure modes to verify before claiming\\nThese are advisory lessons from previous supervisor runs. They do not satisfy any gate by themselves.\\n1. [FM-1.1] Disobey task specification (source_run_id=40f4ecea-e8bd-4639-aec6-27d686743e8f): Repair the planning artifact or traceability gap before invoking the lead again.\\n2. [FM-1.5] Unaware of termination conditions (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Verify this known failure mode explicitly before claiming the gate is complete.\\n3. [FM-2.4] Information withholding (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Address independent reviewer objections with concrete evidence references.\\n4. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\\n5. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=d84b43e3-70de-4f95-b2dc-c7f9aca8684f): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\",\n  \"lead_skill\": null,\n  \"outcome_validation_policy\": {\n    \"fidelity_failure\": \"abort_to_operator\",\n    \"malformed_outcome\": \"retry_once_with_corrective_packet\",\n    \"subproce